00:30:38,253 --> 00:30:41,798
Emma cuma boleh masuk kumpulan
kalau salah seorang tak ada.

481
00:30:42,382 --> 00:30:44,717
Abel pula macam dah tak ada harapan.

482
00:30:46,219 --> 00:30:47,220
Jadi?

483
00:30:47,804 --> 00:30:49,681
Pelaku dalam kes begini biasanya…

484
00:30:52,100 --> 00:30:53,601
orang yang paling banyak untung.

485
00:30:58,898 --> 00:31:01,776
Dalam kes ini, Emma orangnya.

486
00:31:10,785 --> 00:31:13,037
Aduh. Saya harap tak jadi begini,

487
00:31:13,121 --> 00:31:15,290
tapi gerak hati saya selalu tepat.

488
00:31:16,875 --> 00:31:17,959
Hei, Ko Jong-seok!

489
00:31:22,088 --> 00:31:23,339
Nampak?

490
00:31:23,423 --> 00:31:25,425
Tepat lagi.

491
00:31:28,761 --> 00:31:30,471
Apa kita nak buat sekarang, I-rang?

492
00:31:30,555 --> 00:31:32,515
Ko Jong-seok akan datang ke tempat saya.

493
00:31:32,599 --> 00:31:34,350
Saya nak awak tunggu dekat situ

494
00:31:34,434 --> 00:31:36,811
dan tahan dia
apabila dia lari daripada saya.

495
00:31:36,895 --> 00:31:39,772
Awak nak saya tahan dia?

496
00:31:39,856 --> 00:31:41,691
Mesti awak pernah jadi watak detektif.

497
00:31:42,233 --> 00:31:43,651
Awak hafal hak Miranda, bukan?

498
00:31:45,528 --> 00:31:46,487
Kau siapa?

499
00:31:47,155 --> 00:31:49,657
Detektif Yoon Bong-su,
Jenayah Berat Polis Gangnam.

500
00:31:49,741 --> 00:31:52,452
Awak ditahan atas kesalahan
rompakan dan pembunuhan.

501
00:31:52,535 --> 00:31:54,954
Awak berhak untuk senyap.

502
00:31:55,038 --> 00:31:58,750
Awak ada hak untuk upah peguam.

503
00:31:58,833 --> 00:31:59,792
Jangan bergerak.

504
00:32:07,675 --> 00:32:09,594
Pak cik, cepat!

505
00:32:12,722 --> 00:32:13,681
Jangan bergerak!

506
00:32:23,358 --> 00:32:25,276
Tak ada gunanya lari.

507
00:32:26,277 --> 00:32:28,196
Siapa awak nak cakap begitu?

508
00:32:28,863 --> 00:32:29,739
Saya?

509
00:32:30,323 --> 00:32:31,741
Saya dah cakap. Peguam Su-a.

510
00:32:33,701 --> 00:32:36,162
Dia tak ada peguam. Dia dah mati!

511
00:32:36,245 --> 00:32:39,958
Orang mati pun perlukan peguam
kalau mereka mati teraniaya.

512
00:32:40,708 --> 00:32:43,628
Jom, awak kena dihukum
atas perbuatan awak.

513
00:32:45,838 --> 00:32:47,298
Pak cik, tunggu.

514
00:32:49,133 --> 00:32:51,427
Boleh tanya kenapa dia bunuh saya?

515
00:32:51,511 --> 00:32:52,887
Tak ada gunanya sekarang.

516
00:32:56,432 --> 00:32:58,059
Kami kawan baik.

517
00:32:59,268 --> 00:33:01,062
Saya nak tahu kenapa dia bunuh saya.

518
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:06,317
Okey, saya tanya dia.

519
00:33:07,694 --> 00:33:09,195
Apa masalah dia? Seramnya.

520
00:33:09,779 --> 00:33:12,991
Su-a nak tahu kenapa awak bunuh dia.

521
00:33:15,368 --> 00:33:17,245
Awak memang gila, ya?

522
00:33:17,328 --> 00:33:19,080
Dulu kamu berkawan.

523
00:33:20,331 --> 00:33:21,416
Kenapa awak bunuh kawan?

524
00:33:21,499 --> 00:33:22,542
Kawan?

525
00:33:23,918 --> 00:33:24,877
Sudahlah.

526
00:33:26,379 --> 00:33:30,341
Saya tak pernah anggap Su-a kawan.

527
00:33:31,718 --> 00:33:34,095
Kita berkawan dengan orang setaraf.

528
00:33:35,972 --> 00:33:38,141
Awak rasa dia setaraf saya?

529
00:33:47,817 --> 00:33:50,778
<i>Saya ambil banyak kelas</i>
<i>atas sokongan ibu bapa.</i>

530
00:33:50,862 --> 00:33:52,697
<i>Apa saya buat, semuanya menjadi.</i>

531
00:33:53,322 --> 00:33:54,657
<i>Saya seronok di situ,</i>

532
00:33:55,533 --> 00:33:57,326
<i>sampailah Su-a masuk agensi.</i>

533
00:33:57,410 --> 00:34:00,788
Helo, nama saya Kim Su-a.
Sila tunjuk ajar.

534
00:34:01,789 --> 00:34:04,959
<i>Pakaian dia lagi teruk</i>
<i>daripada kain buruk,</i>

535
00:34:05,043 --> 00:34:06,544
<i>tapi dia tak peduli.</i>

536
00:34:09,255 --> 00:34:10,673
Saya akan buat yang terbaik!

537
00:34:12,050 --> 00:34:15,094
<i>Dia bangga sebab ada tiga kerja sambilan.</i>

538
00:34:15,845 --> 00:34:18,848
JUS EPAL

539
00:34:26,564 --> 00:34:29,233
Maaf sebab marah tadi.

540
00:34:30,109 --> 00:34:33,112
Saya tak boleh kawal marah.

541
00:34:33,821 --> 00:34:34,697
Saya minta maaf.

542
00:34:35,656 --> 00:34:39,118
Kalau nak saya maafkan,
ajar saya main gitar.

543
00:34:40,578 --> 00:34:42,413
Senang tulis lagu kalau tahu kod.

544
00:34:46,292 --> 00:34:47,460
Okey.

545
00:34:47,543 --> 00:34:49,545
<i>Su-a suka marah macam tak sedar diri,</i>

546
00:34:49,629 --> 00:34:51,464
<i>tapi anehnya, gadis lain suka dia.</i>

547
00:34:52,423 --> 00:34:54,425
<i>Senang saja mereka maafkan dia.</i>

548
00:34:55,134 --> 00:34:57,512
<i>Mereka faham dan suka dia.</i>

549
00:34:58,846 --> 00:34:59,889
<i>Sakit hati saya.</i>

550
00:35:00,932 --> 00:35:02,391
{\an8}EMMA
KEDUDUKAN AKHIR: KETUJUH, B

551
00:35:02,475 --> 00:35:04,477
{\an8}- Loanne!
- Hebatnya awak, Loanne!

552
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:05,645
{\an8}PERTAMA, 96 MATA
LOANNE

553
00:35:05,728 --> 00:35:07,814
<i>Skor Su-a sentiasa lebih tinggi.</i>

554
00:35:08,773 --> 00:35:11,067
<i>Saya tak boleh lawan</i>
<i>bakat semula jadi dia,</i>

555
00:35:11,776 --> 00:35:13,444
<i>tak kira segigih mana saya berusaha.</i>

556
00:35:14,278 --> 00:35:15,822
<i>Tak adil betul.</i>

557
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,620
Emma, tahniah.

558
00:35:22,703 --> 00:35:24,580
Kita boleh buat debut bersama-sama.

559
00:35:25,248 --> 00:35:26,874
<i>Saya rasa macam nak koyak mulut dia.</i>

560
00:35:26,958 --> 00:35:28,167
Jom makan <i>tteokbokki.</i>

561
00:35:28,251 --> 00:35:30,878
Saya baru dapat gaji. Jom saya belanja.

562
00:35:31,546 --> 00:35:32,672
- Seronoknya.
- Jom?

563
00:35:32,755 --> 00:35:33,714
<i>Kau memang setan.</i>

564
00:35:34,298 --> 00:35:37,510
<i>Setan yang suka cari pasal dengan aku.</i>

565
00:35:38,636 --> 00:35:41,097
<i>Aku dihantui</i>
<i>Resah setiap malam</i>

566
00:35:41,180 --> 00:35:43,349
<i>Tapi kini aku akan jadi bintang</i>

567
00:35:43,432 --> 00:35:44,559
Habis!

568
00:35:45,184 --> 00:35:47,019
Biar betul!

569
00:35:48,271 --> 00:35:50,481
Macam mana awak tulis lirik begitu?

570
00:35:50,565 --> 00:35:53,109
Emma, awak jangan
beritahu orang lain, okey?

571
00:35:53,734 --> 00:35:54,777
Nanti saya fikir.

572
00:35:55,570 --> 00:35:57,780
{\an8}BUNGA INDAH,
JANGAN MENGALAH, JALAN TERANG…

573
00:35:57,864 --> 00:35:59,699
Mungkin awak betul-betul genius.

574
00:36:00,658 --> 00:36:03,369
Taklah, saya tulis sebab bosan saja.

575
00:36:05,788 --> 00:36:08,291
Saya nak lagu ini, boleh?

576
00:36:09,250 --> 00:36:11,794
Boleh ceriakan saya kalau sedih.

577
00:36:11,878 --> 00:36:12,712
Okey.

578
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,423
Tapi jangan beri orang lain.

579
00:36:19,177 --> 00:36:21,762
<i>- Saya kumpul lagu dia satu demi satu.</i>
- Ini pun.

580
00:36:23,055 --> 00:36:24,640
Awak tulis semua ini?

581
00:36:26,392 --> 00:36:28,311
Saya tulis sebab bosan saja.

582
00:36:28,853 --> 00:36:29,937
Macam budak-budak tak?

583
00:36:30,938 --> 00:36:33,065
Budak-budak? Tak, hebat.

584
00:36:34,066 --> 00:36:36,402
Sebenarnya, ini boleh jadi
lagu debut awak.

585
00:36:38,279 --> 00:36:39,572
- Yakah?
- Ya!

586
00:36:39,655 --> 00:36:43,159
<i>Sejak itu, saya mula ada</i>
<i>banyak sebab untuk singkirkan dia.</i>

587
00:36:43,743 --> 00:36:45,953
Dia bukan ketua pun.

588
00:36:46,037 --> 00:36:48,164
Saya tak tahan hadap perangai dia.

589
00:36:48,247 --> 00:36:52,168
Kita cakap kita semua tarik diri
kalau dia tak tarik diri.

590
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,837
CEO terpaksa ikut

591
00:36:54,921 --> 00:36:56,881
sebab ayah saya banyak melabur.

592
00:36:58,174 --> 00:37:01,969
<i>Saya ugut mereka dan paksa</i>
<i>Su-a tarik diri daripada uji bakat.</i>

593
00:37:03,721 --> 00:37:05,848
<i>Semuanya mengikut rancangan.</i>

594
00:37:10,978 --> 00:37:12,772
<i>Saya ikut dia ke bumbung</i>

595
00:37:12,855 --> 00:37:15,066
<i>sebab saya nak tengok dia menangis.</i>

596
00:37:16,692 --> 00:37:20,821
<i>Mesti puas rasanya</i>
<i>kalau tengok dia merana.</i>

597
00:37:37,713 --> 00:37:39,006
Kenapa dia senyum?

598
00:37:40,091 --> 00:37:43,344
<i>Dia tersingkir daripada uji bakat,</i>
<i>tapi kenapa nampak gembira?</i>

599
00:37:45,012 --> 00:37:46,097
<i>Tolaklah dia.</i>

600
00:37:47,348 --> 00:37:48,182
Apa?

601
00:37:48,266 --> 00:37:49,225
<i>Tolak dia.</i>

602
00:37:50,142 --> 00:37:51,852
<i>Tak cukup sekadar disingkirkan.</i>

603
00:37:52,645 --> 00:37:55,314
<i>Perempuan itu akan datang lagi</i>

604
00:37:55,398 --> 00:37:57,108
<i>dan menyusahkan kau lagi.</i>

605
00:37:58,109 --> 00:38:02,321
<i>Macam mana kalau orang tahu</i>
<i>dia yang tulis semua lagu itu?</i>

606
00:38:02,822 --> 00:38:04,031
Ini tak boleh jadi.

607
00:38:05,408 --> 00:38:09,537
<i>Ya. Kalau dia mati,</i>
<i>kau dapat semua lagu dia.</i>

608
00:38:11,205 --> 00:38:13,416
<i>Tolak dia dan ambil telefon dia. Sekarang!</i>

609
00:38:32,226 --> 00:38:33,894
- Awak…
- Tak.

610
00:38:35,146 --> 00:38:36,022
…tolak Su-a?

611
00:38:36,105 --> 00:38:37,523
Saya kata tak!

612
00:38:41,485 --> 00:38:43,571
Saya kena laporkan. Awak bunuh Su-a!

613
00:38:44,530 --> 00:38:45,740
Betulkah saya bunuh dia?

614
00:38:46,574 --> 00:38:47,658
Apa?

615
00:38:47,742 --> 00:38:49,410
Awak yang nak curi lagu dia.

616
00:38:50,328 --> 00:38:51,787
Awak merepek apa?

617
00:38:51,871 --> 00:38:54,290
Su-a yang tulis lagu debut itu.

618
00:38:54,373 --> 00:38:55,958
Awak kata awak tulis.

619
00:38:56,042 --> 00:38:57,168
Yakah?

620
00:38:57,251 --> 00:38:58,586
Tak ingat pun.

621
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:00,588
Buatlah laporan.

622
00:39:00,671 --> 00:39:03,090
Nanti saya cakap awak curi lagu dia.

623
00:39:04,425 --> 00:39:05,843
Awak ingat saya nak diam saja?

624
00:39:05,926 --> 00:39:08,387
Buatlah apa awak nak!

625
00:39:09,472 --> 00:39:11,807
Polis takkan percaya kata awak

626
00:39:12,433 --> 00:39:15,102
dengan saman pelanggaran hak cipta itu.

627
00:39:24,195 --> 00:39:27,948
Su-a percayakan En. Ko.

628
00:39:30,910 --> 00:39:33,204
Tapi dia… Su-a…

629
00:39:43,672 --> 00:39:44,590
Macam mana?

630
00:39:47,218 --> 00:39:48,469
Awak dah gila.

631
00:39:56,018 --> 00:39:59,230
Banyak lagu dia
disimpan dalam telefon ini.

632
00:40:00,648 --> 00:40:03,943
Awak tak boleh tulis lagu
tanpa ciplak lagu orang.

633
00:40:06,737 --> 00:40:08,114
Dengan ini,

634
00:40:09,115 --> 00:40:11,409
kita tak perlu takut apa-apa.

635
00:40:15,996 --> 00:40:16,997
Tergamak…

636
00:40:19,708 --> 00:40:21,335
Tergamak awak buat begitu?

637
00:40:23,796 --> 00:40:25,798
Saya ingatkan kita kawan.

638
00:40:28,843 --> 00:40:30,052
Apa masalah awak?

639
00:40:30,678 --> 00:40:31,679
Dah gila?

640
00:40:33,848 --> 00:40:35,516
Salah saya sebab miskin?

641
00:40:36,892 --> 00:40:39,353
Atau sebab saya boleh
buat semua itu sendiri?

642
00:40:39,437 --> 00:40:40,980
Jangan dekatlah, gila.

643
00:40:42,356 --> 00:40:43,774
Tutup mulut kau!

644
00:40:43,858 --> 00:40:46,694
Saya seronok dapat buat debut dengan awak.

645
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:50,322
Sampai terasa macam mimpi.

646
00:40:50,906 --> 00:40:53,117
Kau cakap apa, gila?

647
00:40:56,412 --> 00:40:58,622
Kau siapa?

648
00:40:59,081 --> 00:40:59,915
Saya?

649
00:41:00,541 --> 00:41:01,917
Peguam agensi awak.

650
00:41:04,336 --> 00:41:05,796
Peguam agensi saya?

651
00:41:06,505 --> 00:41:07,590
Jangan suka sangat.

652
00:41:08,382 --> 00:41:10,259
Saya tak nak tolong pembunuh.

653
00:41:10,968 --> 00:41:13,095
Siapa kau panggil pembunuh?

654
00:41:16,557 --> 00:41:18,476
Ko Jong-seok dah mengaku semuanya.

655
00:41:18,559 --> 00:41:20,144
Kami jumpa telefon Su-a juga.

656
00:41:20,811 --> 00:41:22,229
Awak takkan terlepas kali ini.

657
00:41:25,608 --> 00:41:27,568
Buat apa lagi? Bangunlah.

658
00:41:32,865 --> 00:41:33,741
Awak menangis?

659
00:41:34,658 --> 00:41:36,327
Siapa menangis?

660
00:41:56,347 --> 00:42:00,226
Ramai orang hantar mesej ucap takziah.

661
00:42:02,269 --> 00:42:03,312
Abel pun hantar.

662
00:42:04,104 --> 00:42:04,939
Dia tulis apa?

663
00:42:06,649 --> 00:42:08,526
Dia tahu awak tulis lagu.

664
00:42:11,403 --> 00:42:12,446
<i>Kepada Su-a.</i>

665
00:42:13,822 --> 00:42:14,657
<i>Su-a,</i>

666
00:42:15,241 --> 00:42:18,702
<i>saya suka lagu yang awak tulis</i>

667
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:23,415
<i>sebab saya sentiasa dapat rasa</i>
<i>kehangatan dan harapan dalam lagu awak.</i>

668
00:42:24,667 --> 00:42:28,796
Tak tahu pula dia rasa begini.

669
00:42:29,672 --> 00:42:33,467
Kalau kita ikhlas, orang dapat rasa.

670
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:38,639
Sekarang, nak cari
nombor telefon mak awak?

671
00:42:41,267 --> 00:42:43,227
Mesti ada dalam sejarah panggilan.

672
00:42:44,311 --> 00:42:45,312
Ya.

673
00:42:45,396 --> 00:42:48,232
{\an8}SEJARAH PANGGILAN
MAK

674
00:42:48,315 --> 00:42:49,400
Ini dia.

675
00:42:53,988 --> 00:42:55,155
MAK

676
00:42:55,239 --> 00:42:57,491
Sekejap, pak cik.

677
00:42:58,033 --> 00:42:58,867
Kenapa?

678
00:43:00,077 --> 00:43:04,290
Pak cik rasa dia patut tahu saya dah mati?

679
00:43:05,374 --> 00:43:07,209
Awak tak nak jumpa dia?

680
00:43:08,294 --> 00:43:09,837
Nak, tapi…

681
00:43:15,301 --> 00:43:16,719
Macam mana kalau begini?

682
00:43:16,802 --> 00:43:20,431
Saya guna nombor ini
untuk cari lokasi dia.

683
00:43:21,015 --> 00:43:24,310
Kemudian, awak tengok dia dari jauh.

684
00:43:25,978 --> 00:43:27,146
Okey, pak cik.

685
00:43:32,276 --> 00:43:34,612
HOSPITAL HOSEONG SEOUL

686
00:43:38,782 --> 00:43:39,783
Okey.

687
00:43:41,201 --> 00:43:42,911
Mata puan semakin teruk.

688
00:43:43,621 --> 00:43:44,913
Okey.

689
00:43:44,997 --> 00:43:47,625
Puan ada paling lama sebulan
sebelum buta sepenuhnya.

690
00:43:47,708 --> 00:43:49,293
Tak sempat cari penderma.

691
00:43:50,502 --> 00:43:51,545
Okey.

692
00:43:51,629 --> 00:43:54,923
Dah jumpa orang yang puan nak jumpa itu?

693
00:43:58,177 --> 00:43:59,178
Belum lagi.

694
00:44:00,012 --> 00:44:01,388
Puan kena cepat.

695
00:44:02,389 --> 00:44:04,391
Makin lama, makin teruk mata puan.

696
00:44:05,643 --> 00:44:06,477
Okey.

697
00:44:21,367 --> 00:44:22,534
Mak…

698
00:44:33,629 --> 00:44:35,506
Menurut rekod perubatan dia,

699
00:44:36,131 --> 00:44:40,594
dia didiagnosis dengan
keratitis viral 18 tahun lepas.

700
00:44:43,472 --> 00:44:45,808
Lapan belas tahun lepas?

701
00:44:46,850 --> 00:44:48,519
Umur saya setahun ketika itu.

702
00:44:50,646 --> 00:44:51,814
{\an8}SUSU BAYI

703
00:45:00,948 --> 00:45:02,241
Aduh!

704
00:45:02,324 --> 00:45:03,742
Su-a, kamu okey?

705
00:45:04,743 --> 00:45:05,744
Alamak.

706
00:45:05,828 --> 00:45:07,746
- Mak minta maaf.
<i>- Dia nak nenek jaga saya…</i>

707
00:45:07,830 --> 00:45:08,789
Su-a.

708
00:45:08,872 --> 00:45:10,999
<i>…sebab nak lindungi saya.</i>

709
00:45:11,083 --> 00:45:12,418
WAJAH BAHARU GLORY, KIM SU-A

710
00:45:12,501 --> 00:45:14,169
{\an8}ANAK MAK, SU-A YANG TERBAIK

711
00:45:20,717 --> 00:45:22,469
SU-A ANAKKU SAYANG

712
